parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the airbag warning light can indicate a faulty airbag system, which can lead to the failure of the airbags to deploy in the event of an accident, potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light remains illuminated
the passenger seatbelt buckle light flickers on and off
the airbag light turns on and off intermittently
the airbag light stays on constantly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger OCS can cause the airbag to deploy unnecessarily, potentially causing injuries or fatalities, or fail to deploy in the event of an accident, also potentially causing injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag warning light remains illuminated
the passenger seatbelt buckle light flickers on and off
the airbag light turns on and off intermittently
the airbag light stays on constantly
the passenger OCS sensor is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake light switch does not function correctly
the brake lights flash erratically
the brake pedal feels soft or spongy
the vehicle is difficult to control while braking.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sun visor can cause obstruction of the driver's view, leading to accidents or near-misses.
symptoms: The sun visor falls down or will not stay up
obstructing the driver's view
causing distractions
and impairing vision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the air bag warning light can cause distraction and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The air bag warning light illuminates
indicating a potential problem with the air bag system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The visual distortion on the windshield can cause driver distraction and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The windshield has visual distortions along the lower and side edges
causing driver distraction and discomfort.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The illumination of the seat belt warning light can cause distraction and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: The seat belt warning light illuminates
indicating a potential problem with the seat belt system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear suspension can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Rear control arms rotted out
subframe corrosion
loud bang and scraping sound
rear crossmember detached
vehicle sways and bounces on the road
rear wheel tilted
loss of control
and difficulty maneuvering.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the front suspension can cause loss of control, accidents, and damage to the vehicle.
symptoms: Front suspension "wheel control fork" bolts come loose
causing a knocking noise
and loss of control; front sub-frame corrosion; and front wheel shifts to the rear
causing steering issues.

symptoms: Airbag light stays on
driver seat belt doesn't always securely click down

and electronic stability control sensor illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: These issues can cause inconvenience, discomfort, and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Traction control light illuminates
vehicle vibrates and shakes
